data.description: WELCOME HOME! Finally a chance to own an affordable 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the award winning Los Alamitos School District. This property is loaded with upgrades and amenities. Downstairs you are welcomed with genuine hickory wood flooring in the living room, crown moldings and plantation shutters. The kitchen has recessed lighting, quartz counter tops, porcelain tile flooring, ranch style sink and upgraded cabinets. The entire house has been freshly painted and comes equipped with new baseboards. Stainless steel appliances are available in the kitchen and in the garage you will find a brand new washer and dryer. Upstairs is four spacious bedrooms for your growing family. Two full bathrooms upstairs with brand new vanities and hardware. In the master bedroom you can enjoy a partial mountain view. I almost forgot to mention that all the windows were recently replaced. The improvements are to many to list. Outside you will enjoy a nice private patio and quiet retreat. This property is nestled far inside the complex, is very secure, and has one of best locations in the community. Enjoy the greenbelts that run through the complex and take advantage of community pool and Cabana.  The garage has ample room for storage and has two garage doors so you can close the carport and garage separately and has an extra assigned parking space right in front of the unit. Walking distance to elementary, middle and Los Alamitos High. Please call to  schedule a showing soon. This one will not last long.
